column1: #Text=The Dallas Mavericks defeated the Los Angeles Lakers , 122 - 73 , at American Airlines Center on Wednesday .
#Text=Dallas was expected to win this game easily and they left no doubt with this result .
#Text=In fact , the Mavericks led for the entirety of the second half , as they led by 11 at times in the second half .
#Text=Defense was key for the Mavericks , as they held the Lakers to 38 percent shooting and forced them to commit 17 turnovers .
#Text=Justin Anderson led the way for Dallas in scoring , as he dropped 19 points off the bench .
#Text=Justin Anderson led the team in scoring off the bench , as he dropped 19 points on 5 - of - 11 shooting .
#Text=Deron Williams was the only other starter in double figures , as he accumulated 13 points , five rebounds and eight assists .
